<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/9688> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #9688" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/10> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "ref. 517" .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/7794> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #7794" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/5> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Q(uaestor) P(ro praetore?), with M. Barbatius Q. P., and M. Nerva Proq. P. In MRR 2.372, refer also to Crawford, RRC 1.525-526, no. 517, 41 B.C.\n" .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/6495> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #6495" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "His title is not preserved. He commanded the right wing of Antony's fleet at Actium (Vell. 2.85.2; Plut. Ant. 65.1; 66.2-3; see Gardthausen 1.382; 2.197, note 32)." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/6361> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #6361" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "CIL 11.6673, 19; Fast. Cap., Degrassi 58f. (L. G[elliu]s L. f. L. n. [-]), 135, 506f.; Fast. Mag. Vic., ibid. 282, 288; Fast. Biond., ibid. 291f. Q-] Cocceiu[s -]); Dio 49, Index, and 1.1, and 24.1; Chr. 354; Fast. Hyd.; Chr. Pasc.; Cassiod.; and on Cocceius, ILS 8780; SEG 4.604, Consul Designate; see PIR² 2.290, no. 1224; De Laet no. 120." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/6225> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #6225" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Q(uaestor) P(ro Praetore?) under Antony in the East ca. 41 (Grueber, CRRBM?,.493)." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/10484> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #10484" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/21> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Liv. Per. 122, Dio 47.24.3-6.. Friend of Brutus. Conspired against both Brutus and Cassius in Asia in 42 despite being a member of the liberators' camp. He was left unpunished and released, for the sake of his brother and mother, whereupon he went over to Octavian and Antony." .
